headline: Q4 Earnings Roundup: Transcat (NASDAQ:TRNS) And The Rest Of The Maintenance and Repair Distributors Segment
summary: As the Q4 earnings season comes to a close, it’s time to take stock of this quarter’s best and worst performers in the maintenance and repair distributors industry, including Transcat (NASDAQ:TRNS) and its peers.
